Initially from http://psitsmike.com/2011/10/node-js-and-socket-io-multiroom-chat-tutorial/

1. Install NodeJS and npm
2. Execute 'npm install -d' to create the node_modules folder from package.json
3. Run program 'node app.js'

Modified to use JQuery Mobile

Very rough UI.

Functionality:
1. Create User
  Caches name in browser (added)
2. Join Chat room
  Wipes chat log when switching rooms (added)
3. Create new chat room (added)
  Can create new room, which automatically joins you to that room once created. Room name also appears on sidebar

